These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, ivory, chestnut, black
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, balloon-flower, sunflower, marigold
4 different games are played: domino, chess, whist, mah-jongg
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, gardening, dancing, reading
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, milk, fanta
 1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 2. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person drinking fanta##2
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person drinking fanta##1
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person drinking tea is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person playing whist##2
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is the person who likes chestnut##1
 8. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Color           | chestnut | aquamarine   | black | ivory |
| Flower   | rose      | balloon-flower | sunflower              | marigold |
| Game   | domino       | chess     | mah-jongg               | whist    |
| Hobby           | gardening        | dancing     | reading           | magic-tricks       |
| Beverage     | lemonade | milk     | tea                | fanta      |

