There are 4 different nationalities: australian, dutch, spanish, american
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, documentary, satire, crime
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, november, october, march
City: rome, paris, marseilles, liverpool
 1. the spanish is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the dutch is between the person driving the roller and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 4. the person watching crime movies is the person traveling to rome##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is the dutch##1
 6. the spanish is on the left of the australian##1
 7. the american is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the spanish##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the australian##1
10. the spanish is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the person traveling to rome is the person driving the roller##1
12. the person driving the tram is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Transport          | roller       | scooter      | tram      | taxi      |
| Nationality           | american | dutch | spanish | australian |
| Movie-Genre   | crime          | documentary       | satire            | zombie      |
| Birthday           | august            | october    | november           | march       |
| City         | rome        | paris    | marseilles         | liverpool  |

