4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, siglo, dunhill, aristoff
There 4 different types of food: orange, spinach, potato, pumpkin
4 different pets are kept: horse, chinchilla, fish, turtle
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, russian, british, egyptian
 1. the game-smoker is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person eating spinach and the british##2
 3. the person eating potato is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing scrabble##2
 4. the turkish is the siglo-smoker##1
 5. the owner of the fish is the aristoff-smoker##1
 6. the person eating potato is the person playing snooker##1
 7. the egyptian is the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the person playing snooker is on the right of the russian##1
 9. the person eating potato is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
10. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
11. the owner of the turtle is between the aristoff-smoker and the egyptian##2
12. the owner of the chinchilla is between the turkish and the person playing snooker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Game      | scrabble      | snooker         | backgammon | mah-jongg      |
| Cigar           | aristoff | dunhill | game | siglo     |
| Food   | pumpkin         | potato          | orange  | spinach |
| Pet         | fish        | turtle  | chinchilla | horse   |
| Nationality     | russian    | british         | egyptian     | turkish     |

