.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
City: prague, rome, new-york, nizza
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, brown, chestnut, azure
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, may, february
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, dahlia, amaryllis, poppy
House: victorian, ranch-style, cottage, colonial
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who growsamaryllis and the ranch-style house##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is the cottage house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 7. the person traveling to prague is the person who likes azure##1
 8. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 9. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
10. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the victorian house##1
11. the person traveling to nizza is between the person who likes azure and the person who growslily##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |   4    |
