The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, crime, animation, superhero
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, cain, bluemaster, ritmeester
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, mauve, grey, yellow
4 different pets are kept: pony, frog, rabbit, hamster
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is the person watching crime movies##1
 2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 3. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who likes yellow and the ritmeester-smoker##2
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is the person who likes apricot##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing mah-jongg and the owner of the hamster##2
 6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 7. the person who likes grey is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the game-smoker##1
10. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1

