.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
House: cottage, palace, gothic-revival, colonial
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, december, april, march
City: paris, miami, hamburg, colone
4 different games are played: domino, chess, scrabble, whist
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, water, cola
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person traveling to miami##1
 2. the person drinking cola is between the person traveling to colone and the person playing domino##2
 3. the person drinking lemonade is between the person playing chess and the person drinking water##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the left of the colonial house##1
 7. the palace house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing scrabble##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking water##1
10. the cottage house is the person traveling to paris##1
11. the person traveling to paris is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| House         | gothic-revival  | palace | colonial | cottage |
| Birthday   | march      | december   | april      | june    |
| City   | miami  | hamburg | colone        | paris     |
| Game         | domino  | chess  | scrabble     | whist      |
| Beverage     | iced-tea | cola      | lemonade   | water       |

 